textBody: Cell Cycle is a biweekly peer-reviewed scientific journal covering cell biology. The editor-in-chief is Mikhail V. Blagosklonny (Roswell Park Cancer Institute). The journal is abstracted and indexed in Medline/PubMed and the Science Citation Index Expanded.
